# Local-model demo: free, keyless, Ollama.
# Regenerate: vhs demo/local.tape
Output demo/local.gif
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 620
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "aerin -m ollama/qwen2.5-coder"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Type "explain what src/core/agent.ts does in two sentences"
Enter
Sleep 15s
Type "/exit"
Enter
Sleep 1s
